narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: This course gave an overview of the major branches of Arabic scientific thought in the Middle Ages through the lens of al-Khwarizmi's Mafatih al-'ulum. We also worked on critical reading skills and discussed general topics relating to Arabic and Islamic studies.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: This was an amazing course! If you're able to handle it and willing to put in the work, you will gain a ton from it. My only caution is that this class is way more work than any undergrad class I've taken.
